  <brief_title>Respiratory Care in Intensive Care Unit for Neuromuscular Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Modalities of Respiratory Care, Vital and Respiratory Prognosis in Neuromuscular Patients Admitted to an Intensive Care Unit for Respiratory Failure</official_title>
