  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Retrospective multicentric observational study exploring the population of adult
      neuromuscular patients presenting a respiratory distress requiring their admission in an
      Intensive Care Unit (ICU) for ventilatory support.

      Research of markers associated with long term mortality and ventilatory status.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
